{"tid":388983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屎坑馬不認同港鐵故障多 列車準確率維持99.9%","createTime":"2017-09-06T00:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T07:34:05.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d777168514d04aac1d5b912263690224d12571e","tid":388983,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T00:09:54.000Z","msg":"馬時亨不認同港鐵故障多 列車準確率維持99.9%<br />\n<br />\n香港電台-港聞<br />\n4月23日週六上午9:39<br />\n<br />\n對於有人批評港鐵故障多，港鐵主席馬時亨不認同。他說港鐵在2000年時每日平均有2000架次列車，但到今年就增加至每日平均8000架次，列車的準確率維持在99.9%。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨出席一個電台節目時又表示，港鐵的載客量已近飽和，如果再減票價令乘客量上升，服務將更難維持質素。港鐵已利用改善信號系統等措施，希望進一步加密班次。他說港鐵在這方面的表現屬全球最佳，市民應引以為傲。"},{"pid":"4eaf4b489f59eb4e4da4bd0d8ff4f80d4972aa8e","tid":388983,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T00:13:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾馬"},{"pid":"565f3e00c4fa4f244146fcd54a094c2c6f9e0342","tid":388983,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T00:58:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思囉 下年再加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d73b1f62e983147fec9397beda8509815f691c8","tid":388983,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1431d3aaff8f603e30dc0c7a2ddfd029d8ef8aa","tid":388983,"uid":130117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:14:14.000Z","msg":"2000年幾多條線，而家幾多條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a0a71db5065b77ad9adf96ef2a36e4df058044","tid":388983,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f848b53d1f69aa49aa32376257c2631acab19cb","tid":388983,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:22:32.000Z","msg":"又壞"},{"pid":"0802b88a03fe2bbffe4a29cac2acfe0916fe9fab","tid